<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Verify Your Account</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      color: #333;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .container {
      background: #fff;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: auto;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #fff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }

    .code {
      font-size: 1.4em;
      font-weight: bold;
      background-color: #eee;
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      font-size: 0.85em;
      color: #777;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Hello {{names}},</h2>
    <p>Thank you for signing up with us!</p>

    <p>Please use the verification code below to verify your account:</p>

    <p class="code">{{verificationCode}}</p>

    <p>Or you can click the button below to go to the verification page:</p>

    <a href="{{url}}" class="btn">Verify My Account</a>

    <p class="footer">If you did not request this email, please ignore it.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
